<li>partner allowance</li>
<li>widow allowance</li>
<li>benefit <a href="../../../acronyms#pp" title="Parenting payment">PP</a> (partnered)</li>
<li>special benefit</li>
<li><a href="../../../acronyms#abstudy" title="Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander Study Assistance Scheme">ABSTUDY</a> living allowance</li>
</ul></td>
<td>
<p>1061ZK(5)(a)</p>
